:55.000Z","msg":"個閘識自己轉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ffce23ec903608184f83749e3c8dca559feaa3","tid":1654204,"uid":3424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e7610d30ebb06ab130c1195ffe3f43c64a8c65","tid":1654204,"uid":108337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"個閘識自己轉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a5dbc71becb7f232b12a14ebdb195150fa670","tid":1654204,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"27ad14c7913185122da158e51a5bf8fa878fe0d8","tid":1654204,"uid":41736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"跳